Enumerate AWS IAM Policies Using Pacu
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Install and configure the Pacu framework for AWS security testing
Perform IAM policy enumeration using Pacu modules
Identify privilege escalation paths and IAM misconfigurations
Automate enumeration tasks using Python scripts
Generate security assessment reports
Prerequisites
Basic understanding of AWS IAM (users, roles, policies)
Familiarity with Linux command line
Basic Python programming knowledge
Understanding of JSON format
AWS CLI basics
