Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Pacu installation fails

# Update pip and retry
pip3 install --upgrade pip
pip3 install -r requirements.txt --user
Issue: Database connection errors

# Check database file permissions
ls -la /home/ubuntu/pacu/pacu.db
chmod 644 /home/ubuntu/pacu/pacu.db
Issue: Module execution fails

# Verify AWS credentials are loaded
# In Pacu session:
whoami

# Re-import credentials if needed
import_keys --profile default
Issue: Python script errors

# Verify Python version
python3 --version

# Install missing dependencies
pip3 install boto3 botocore
Issue: No data collected

Ensure AWS credentials have appropriate read permissions
Check CloudTrail logs for API call failures
Verify network connectivity to AWS endpoints
